Package com.qtplaf.library.trading.server

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Account
    Access to account information.
    ConnectionListener
    Interface for listeners interested in receiving connection events.
    ConnectionManager
    Interface responsible to manage connections.
    DataIterator
    Iterator interface aimed to download huge amounts of price data.
    FeedManager
    Interface responsible to manage live feeds.
    HistoryManager
    Interface responsible to provide information about the history of data and orders.
    Order
    Contains order data and allows order management.
    OrderHistory
    Contains the partial order close/fill event when an order has been partially closed/filled.
    OrderManager
    Interface responsible to manage orders.
    Server
    Interface resposible to provide access to all the server services.
    TickIterator
    Iterator interface aimed to download huge amounts of tick data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionEvent
    Events generated by the connection manager.
    ServerFactory
    Support for servers has to be hard coded at this stage of development.
    ServerFactory.ServerConnectionListener
    Standard connection listener.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AccountState
    Enumerates possible account states.
    AccountType
    Enumerates the three possible types of accounts.
    OfferSide
    Enumerates the two possible offer sides, ask and bid.
    OrderCommand
    Enumerates the different types of orders.
    OrderMessage
    Enumerates the possible messages received upon order changes.
    OrderState
    Enumerates the possible order states.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ServerException
    Exceptions thrown by the server.
